FILES:
    /etc/ssh/sshd_config (switch ports an root login) --can also allow specific users on AllowUsers
    /etc/ssh/ssh_config (switch ports)

package info    
    (sudo) apt show openssh-server
install openssh-server
    (sudo) apt install openssh-server

check service
    (sudo) service ssh status

restart
    (sudo) service ssh restart

connect
    ssh <user>@localhost -p <portnumber> (here we use 4243 an redirect to 4242)

